6015:{n:"Hereafter",d:"<span style='color:#ffffff'>Hereafter　</span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%s/5<br /></span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>Returns the soul to where it belonged.<br /><br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Thời gian thi triển: 1 giây<br /></span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Weapon Requirement: Fan<br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>Single-Target Blessing</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>",u:"<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d chân khí </span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />Casts a blessing on a single target, granting them a </span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Living Hollow</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> effect that has a </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />chance to revive them within </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây. The target who is revived this way will gain a<br /></span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> movement speed bonus, but they will die after </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây. Increasing the average<br />value of your Resistances will increase the success rate of the blessing. In addition,<br />it also increases the chance to grant immunity against controls to the revived target.<br />Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.</span>"},
6016:{n:"Leaf Storm",d:"<span style='color:#ffffff'>Leaf Storm　</span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%s/7<br /></span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>Unleash a mighty gust that barrels down a group of ranged enemies.<br /><br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Thời gian thi triển: 2 giâys<br /></span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Weapon Requirement: Fan<br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>AOE Attack</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>",u:"<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d chân khí </span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />Attacks enemies within </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>15</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> meters of a target </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>2</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> times. This attack is applied with<br />an additional </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> base Attack Power, plus an additional </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> Attack Power.<br />Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>7</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.</span>"},
6017:{n:"Storm's Grace",d:"<span style='color:#ffffff'>Storm's Grace　</span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%s/5<br /></span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>Infuses the power of the the storm, granting swift speed.<br /><br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Thời gian thi triển: 1 giây<br /></span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Weapon Requirement: Fan<br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>Single-Target Blessing</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>",u:"<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d chân khí </span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />Blesses a single target for </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giâys, increasing their movement speed<br />by </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>1.5</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> yards/giây, while also granting the same effect for yourself.<br />This effect can be stacked up to </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>3</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> times.<br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>Multiple speed effects can stack, but the speed cap is </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>6</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span><span style='color:#11aaff'> yards/giây.</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.</span>"},
6018:{n:"Willow's Dance",d:"<span style='color:#ffffff'>Willow's Dance　</span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%s/5<br /></span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>Increases your speed for a short period of time.<br /><br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Thời gian thi triển: 1 giây<br /></span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Weapon Requirement: Fan<br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>Chúc phúc bản thân</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>",u:"<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d chân khí </span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />For </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giâys, increases your movement speed by </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%.1f</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> yards/giây.<br />Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.</span>"},
6019:{n:"Chilling Wind",d:"<span style='color:#ffffff'>Chilling Wind　</span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%s/5<br /></span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>Blows a chilling wind to slow down an enemy.<br /><br /></span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Thời gian thi triển: 1 giây<br /></span><span style='color:#11ff11'>Weapon Requirement: Fan<br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>Single-Target Attack</span><span style='color:#ffffff'></span>",u:"<span style='color:#ffcb4a'>　</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br /></span><span style='color:#11aaff'>%d chân khí</span><span style='color:#ffffff'><br />Attacks a target with an added </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> Attack Power, plus an additional<br />amount of Attack Power equal to x</span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>10</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> of your Stun Resistance.<br />Also slows down the target by </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d%%</span><span style='color:#ffffff'>. Lasts for </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%d</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.<br />Thời gian hồi kỹ năng: </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>5</span><span style='color:#ffffff'> giây.</span>"},
